Cook fettuccine pasta according to package instructions. 2. In a skillet, heat olive oil and butter over medium heat. 3. Add sliced chicken and cook until golden brown. 4. Add minced garlic and cook until fragrant. 5. Pour in heavy cream and bring to a simmer. 6. Stir in grated parmesan cheese until melted and sauce is creamy. 7. Season with salt and pepper. 8. Toss cooked pasta with the sauce. 9.
